metadata.name: Megalodon Membership #1
metadata.description: This is the Megalodon Membership of the Floor Sharks Club. This gains you access to their Discord Server if you agree to the rules and take the Floor Sharks' Pledge. The Floor Sharks Club is a Diamond Hand Cooperative that pledges to not sell below target floor prices based on the member-created Shark Attack List. Members who sell below that target floor price will lose their privileges as a member.
